The '''List of alluvial sites in Switzerland''', listing the Swiss heritage [[floodplain]]s. It is based on the ''Federal Inventory of Alluvial sites of National Importance'', part of a 1992 Ordinance of the Swiss Federal Council implementing the Federal Law on the Protection of Nature and Cultural Heritage.

